<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_b62d6574-3c8b-4558-8ac1-cd131605c138" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H1F1</sptc><title id="_119b4acb-74a5-44ba-b043-691f30b3e243">Functional Statements</title><archive-num>2019: F2.1</archive-num><subclause id="_bfbee070-9b03-46f1-87e1-1d6727c53719" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9ebf8492-a15e-4a1e-be59-b6b39b3984f4">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building or structure is to withstand the combination of loads and other actions to which it may be reasonably subjected.</p></subclause><subclause id="_1a042a31-b760-4d65-a234-1e7aa65bbb8e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f4a984df-9890-4c13-adcb-f54bfa9e6b92">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Glazing is to be installed in a building to avoid undue risk of injury to people.</p></subclause></clause>